This move is a clear blunder and serves no purpose to White. White has put his king in the open file. And Black also has the opportunity to capture the Rank 2 and then white king is stuck in the very first file it is standing on. This move is the biggest mistake that cost white's game. Always avoid such position. Never let your opponent to restrict your king in the first rank!!!
